OL,3,CFairground operator fined after
OL,4,Crollercoaster worker dies in South
OL,5,CShields
OL,7,FA fairground operator has been fined
OL,8,Ffollowing a man's death weeks after
OL,9,Fsuffering serious head injuries while
OL,10,Fworking on a ride in South Shields.
OL,12,FDean Cariss was struck by a moving car
OL,13,Fon a rollercoaster ride while daily
OL,14,Ftesting and maintenance was being
OL,15,Fcarried out at Ocean Beach Pleasure
OL,16,FPark on 19 March 2023.
OL,18,FThe 52-year-old sustained severe head
OL,19,Finjuries and as a result died in
OL,20,Fhospital 13 days later.
