OL,7,FA Health and Safety Executive (HSE)
OL,8,Finvestigation found that Premier
OL,9,FAttractions Limited had failed to
OL,10,Fensure the health and safety of
OL,11,Femployees. The company pleaded guilty
OL,12,Fand was fined #28,000 at South
OL,13,FTyneside Magistrates Court on 17
OL,14,FDecember 2024.
OL,16,FMr Cariss was a step-father to three
OL,17,Fchildren, a grandparent to nine, and a
OL,18,Fcarer for his partner Helen Wright,
OL,19,Fwho described him as "bubbly and fun".
