OL,7,FIn a written statement provided to the
OL,8,Fcourt, she said: "He was very generous
OL,9,Fand liked to help people.
OL,11,F"My whole life has been turned upside
OL,12,Fdown and back to front. He would move
OL,13,Fheaven and earth for me. He was a big
OL,14,Fpersonality and I miss the fun and
OL,15,Flaughter. Silence is deafening when I
OL,16,Fam in the house on my own.
OL,18,F"Everybody fell in love with him when
OL,19,Fthey met him. There was no serious
OL,20,Fside, just laughter and fun."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
