OL,7,FThe investigation by HSE found that a
OL,8,Fsuitable and sufficient risk
OL,9,Fassessment had not been carried out
OL,10,Fand proper controls had not been
OL,11,Femployed to prevent employees
OL,12,Faccessing dangerous areas whilst the
OL,13,Fride was operating.
OL,15,FPremier Attractions Limited of Little
OL,16,FHulton, Manchester, pleaded guilty to
OL,17,Ffailing to comply with section 2(1) of
OL,18,FThe Health and Safety at Work etc Act
OL,19,F1974. They were fined #28,000 and
OL,20,Fordered to pay #5,976 costs.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
