OL,7,FHSE Inspector William Gilroy said:
OL,8,F"This tragic incident led to the
OL,9,Favoidable death of a caring, family
OL,10,Fman.
OL,12,F"Dean's death could easily have been
OL,13,Fprevented if his employer had acted to
OL,14,Fidentify and manage the risks
OL,15,Finvolved, and to put a safe system of
OL,16,Fwork in place.
OL,18,F"Companies should be aware that HSE
OL,19,Fwill not hesitate to take appropriate
OL,20,Fenforcement action against those who
OL,21,Ffall below the required standards."
